articles.title: The rare 'penis plant' just bloomed for the first time in over two decades - CNN
articles.description: A rare and notoriously difficult "penis plant" (Amorphophallus decus-silvae) has bloomed in a Netherlands botanical garden. This is only the third time the plant has flowered in Europe since another plant of this species bloomed in the garden in 1997.
